[quote name='Renegrade']Probodobodyne RoveMate 2.0!<br>
<br>
Initial draft!<br>
<br>
[code]<br>
// Probodobodyne RoveMate :: Squad/Parts/Utility/roverBody/roverBody.cfg<br>
@PART[roverBody]<br>
{<br>
